title: Dwie Zmiany
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Take-out, European, Fusion, Polish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant, club, and gallery hosting daily concerts and exhibits. Vegan dishes offered include hummus, vegetables and bread as appetizer; salads with oyster mushroom, potato, kale or beet roots; creamy pumpkin soup or tomatoes soup with cheakpeas and as mains: red lentils pie with tomatoes, kale and pumpkin or beets falafel with zucchini, white wine and garlic.
